# Pages Composition & Routing

Compose pages by stitching Litho sections, as specified in [litho.md](mdc:litho.md) and aligned to [frontend.md](mdc:frontend.md).

## Homepage Composition (reference only)
- Hero + unified search: base from `Pages/Home/TravelAgency.jsx` hero. Inject a unified search component (custom) using `Components/Form/*` styles.
- Featured: reuse TravelAgency featured tours and `HotelResort` accommodations blocks.
- Recently listed properties: use portfolio grids from `Pages/Portfolios/*` (e.g., classic/boxed three column) with property meta overlay.
- Investment spotlight: pull stats/CTA from `Pages/Home/Finance.jsx` or charts from `Components/partials/charts/*`.
- Testimonials/newsletter: reuse existing components (`Testimonials`, subscribe forms).

## Section Reuse Map
- Rentals (BnB): `Home/HotelResort.jsx` sections for listing highlights; `Components/ImageGallery/*` for detail; `ModalPopup/*` for booking.
- Tours: `Home/TravelAgency.jsx` sections; use `InfoBanner/*` for categories.
- Properties: `Portfolios/*` grids; `SingleProjectPage*` patterns for detail layout.
- Cars: `Shop/ShopWide.jsx` for grids and `Shop/SingleProduct.jsx` for detail.
- Investment: `Home/Finance.jsx`, `AdditionalPages/PricingPackagesPage.jsx`, `partials/charts/*`.

## Routing Targets (must match frontend.md)
- `/`, `/rentals`, `/rentals/:id`, `/tours`, `/tours/:id`, `/properties`, `/properties/:id`, `/cars`, `/cars/:id`, `/invest`, `/blogs`, `/blogs/:slug`, `/login`, `/register`, `/account`.

## Page Assembly Rules
- Avoid duplicating entire page files; prefer extracting needed sections into composable components.
- Wrap data-driven sections with containers/hooks; pass API data as props to Litho presentational components.
- Keep headers/footers consistent across pages by reusing existing Header/Footer components.

## Litho Page Sections to Reuse
- **Hero Sections**: `Pages/Home/TravelAgency.jsx` - hero slider with package pricing
- **Featured Content**: `Pages/Home/HotelResort.jsx` - accommodation showcases
- **Portfolio Grids**: `Pages/Portfolios/PortfolioClassicThreeColumn.jsx` - for property listings
- **Shop Layouts**: `Pages/Shop/ShopWide.jsx` - for car rentals with filters
- **Blog Sections**: `Pages/Blogs/BlogGrid.jsx` - for content pages
- **Contact Forms**: `Pages/Contact/ContactUsSimplePage.jsx` - for all forms
- **Pricing Tables**: `Pages/AdditionalPages/PricingPackagesPage.jsx` - for investment plans

## Component Extraction Pattern
When reusing Litho sections, extract reusable parts into `Components/`:
```jsx
// Instead of copying entire TravelAgency hero
// Extract to Components/Hero/HeroSlider.jsx
// Then reuse in multiple pages
import HeroSlider from '../../Components/Hero/HeroSlider';
```

## Page Structure Template
Every page should follow this Litho-inspired structure:
```jsx
// Header - reuse existing Header components
<Header />

// Page Title - use PageTitle components
<PageTitle />

// Main Content - compose from Litho sections
<section>...</section>

// Footer - reuse existing Footer components
<Footer />
```

